284
00:13:19,208 --> 00:13:20,833
I can't believe this guy!

285
00:13:20,916 --> 00:13:22,250
Sure he may be
good looking

286
00:13:22,333 --> 00:13:24,500
and extremely successful
at such a young age,

287
00:13:24,583 --> 00:13:27,708
but I have never seen a bigger
narcissist in my life!

288
00:13:27,791 --> 00:13:30,083
From now on your
name is Naru...

289
00:13:30,166 --> 00:13:33,041
As in Naru the Narcissist!

290
00:13:42,500 --> 00:13:43,916
Well that's all we
