291
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,125
For today...?

292
00:13:45,208 --> 00:13:46,208
You mean...!

293
00:13:46,291 --> 00:13:48,208
I'll see you
here tomorrow.

294
00:13:48,291 --> 00:13:49,500
Oh man.

295
