It's kind of a long story.

299
00:14:01,625 --> 00:14:03,625
Paranormal investigations?

300
00:14:03,708 --> 00:14:06,083
So he's not an
upperclassman.

301
00:14:06,166 --> 00:14:08,000
According to him,
he's a ghost hunter.

302
00:14:08,083 --> 00:14:09,416
A ghost hunter?

303
00:14:09,500 --> 00:14:11,958
Mai?

304
00:14:12,041 --> 00:14:14,333
I was wondering if you
would introduce me to him.

305
00:14:14,416 --> 00:14:15,375
Introduce you?

306
00:14:15,458 --> 00:14:16,666
To Naru?

307
00:14:16,750 --> 00:14:18,458
What's this Naru
stuff all about?

308
00:14:18,541 --> 00:14:20,291
That guy has got to be
the biggest narcissist

309
00:14:20,375 --> 00:14:21,708
I've ever met in my life...

310
00:14:21,791 --> 00:14:24,250
I can't believe I actually
have to work for him now!

311
00:14:24,333 --> 00:14:26,666
You know I have many
psychic abilities myself.

312
00:14:26,750 --> 00:14:28,833
And I think I could really
help Kazuya with his work.

313
00:14:28,916 --> 00:14:31,083
You know since he is
a professional and all

314
00:14:31,166 --> 00:14:33,541
maybe it's not such a good
idea for you to get involved.

315
00:14:33,625 --> 00:14:35,375
Well I'm by no
means an amateur!

316
00:14:37,750 --> 00:14:38,916
Let's go, Mai.

317
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:46,500
That girl is
such a weirdo.

318
