00:18:36,625 --> 00:18:37,958
No there isn't.

431
00:18:38,041 --> 00:18:39,958
I don't sense one
paranormal being.

432
00:18:41,291 --> 00:18:42,291
Ghost!

433
00:18:42,375 --> 00:18:44,000
Relax Mai, she's human.

434
00:18:45,166 --> 00:18:47,208
Masako Hara is
a spirit medium.

435
00:18:47,291 --> 00:18:48,625
Oh... Another one?

436
00:18:48,708 --> 00:18:49,958
Fantastic...

437
00:18:50,041 --> 00:18:52,083
So now they're
calling in a t.v. star?

438
00:18:52,166 --> 00:18:53,208
This is ridiculous.

439
00:18:53,291 --> 00:18:55,708
It's easy to fake
results on television.

440
00:18:55,791 --> 00:18:57,083
The only reason
she gets ratings

441
00:18:57,166 --> 00:18:59,291
is because she's pretty and
wears that silly kimono.

442
00:18:59,375 --> 00:19:01,708
Why thank you. I take
that as a compliment.

443
00:19:01,791 --> 00:19:03,750
Well. Trust me... it's not.

444
00:19:03,833 --> 00:19:05,375
Correct me if I'm wrong

445
00:19:05,458 --> 00:19:07,166
but I don't think I've had the
pleasure of meeting you before.

446
00:19:07,250 --> 00:19:08,666
Yes... We have never met,

