00:19:08,750 --> 00:19:10,333
but your reputation
precedes you.

448
00:19:10,416 --> 00:19:11,708
Right.

449
00:19:11,791 --> 00:19:13,541
Anyways, there's
a haunting here.

450
00:19:13,625 --> 00:19:15,125
In my professional
opinion...

