00:19:22,250 --> 00:19:23,958
So you mean like someone
was murdered here

456
00:19:24,041 --> 00:19:25,333
and they have to
spend eternity

457
00:19:25,416 --> 00:19:27,416
searching the halls for
their killer or something?

