00:19:29,250 --> 00:19:30,583
it's going to lose its home,

460
00:19:30,666 --> 00:19:33,208
so it's attempting to
block the construction.

461
00:19:33,291 --> 00:19:35,791
John... What do you think?

462
00:19:35,875 --> 00:19:37,708
Well to be honest,
I'm not sure...

463
00:19:37,791 --> 00:19:39,500
But Usually a haunting
does originate

464
00:19:39,583 --> 00:19:41,791
with a ghost or spirit
occupying a structure.

465
00:19:41,875 --> 00:19:44,458
