466
00:19:44,541 --> 00:19:46,208
or fiction and folklore...

467
00:19:46,291 --> 00:19:47,583
Are you listening, Mai?

468
00:19:47,666 --> 00:19:48,625
Of course I am.

469
00:19:48,708 --> 00:19:50,083
What do you take me for?

470
00:19:50,166 --> 00:19:52,500
These are things
you need to learn.

471
00:19:52,583 --> 00:19:53,916
Enough talk...

472
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:56,500
I'm getting rid of this
thing as soon as I get back.

473
00:19:56,583 --> 00:19:58,833
I don't know how long I could
put up with you people.

474
00:20:00,416 --> 00:20:02,625
I wouldn't be so confident
in your abilities...

475
00:20:02,708 --> 00:20:05,333
The spirit that haunts this
site is incredibly powerful.

476
00:20:05,416 --> 00:20:06,666
Kuroda.

477
00:20:06,750 --> 00:20:08,041
Move aside.

478
00:20:11,625 --> 00:20:13,000
The spirit attacked me.

479
00:20:13,083 --> 00:20:13,750
Huh?

480
00:20:14,500 --> 00:20:15,750
It's true...

481
00:20:15,833 --> 00:20:16,958
I was walking
down the hallway

482
00:20:17,041 --> 00:20:18,791
