was yanked backwards

483
00:20:18,875 --> 00:20:20,291
with amazing force...

484
00:20:20,375 --> 00:20:23,083
When I tried to flee it
started strangling me.

485
00:20:23,166 --> 00:20:25,250
You're interfering
with me, psychic!

486
00:20:25,333 --> 00:20:26,875
Leave or die!

487
00:20:26,958 --> 00:20:28,250
When did this happen?

488
00:20:28,333 --> 00:20:31,125
A few minutes ago in the
second floor hallway.

489
00:20:31,208 --> 00:20:33,000
That's false.
There is no spirit here.

490
00:20:33,083 --> 00:20:34,083
Yes there are...!

491
00:20:34,166 --> 00:20:35,541
There definitely are...!

492
00:20:35,625 --> 00:20:37,166
And they're angry!

493
00:20:37,250 --> 00:20:39,291
You said it was the
second floor hallway?

494
00:21:01,666 --> 00:21:03,666
What just happened?
Is the camera broken?

495
00:21:03,750 --> 00:21:05,916
No... but it is quite strange.

496
00:21:06,916 --> 00:21:08,250
When a spirit
becomes active,

497
00:21:08,333 --> 00:21:10,750
electronic equipment will
often malfunction...

498
00:21:10,833 --> 00:21:12,458
but here I'm not so sure.

499
00:21:12,541 --> 00:21:13,375
Is it...

500
00:21:13,458 --> 00:21:15,625
a spirit or EM
interference.

501
00:21:15,708 --> 00:21:17,291
It's quite
obviously a spirit.

502
00:21:17,375 --> 00:21:19,625
Interference doesn't cause
someone to be attacked.

503
00:21:19,708 --> 00:21:21,875
But Masako said there
are no spirits here..

504
00:21:21,958 --> 00:21:23,791
Well, let's just say that
I'm a little skeptical...

505
00:21:23,875 --> 00:21:25,583
about her.

506
00:21:25,666 --> 00:21:27,291
It's common for
female mediums

507
00:21:27,375 --> 00:21:30,083
to be either exactly
right or way off base.

508
00:21:30,166 --> 00:21:31,958
Even if she can't
sense any spirits

509
00:21:32,041 --> 00:21:34,250
now doesn't mean the
haunting isn't active.

510
00:21:34,333 --> 00:21:35,833
If what you say is true,

511
00:21:35,916 --> 00:21:38,500
then it's possible that the
spirit that inhabits this place

512
00:21:38,583 --> 00:21:40,625
is very in tune with
your wavelength.

513
00:21:40,708 --> 00:21:42,416
Yeah... That's right.

514
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:44,208
If that's the case...

515
00:21:44,291 --> 00:21:45,958
then is this all our fault?

516
00:21:47,166 --> 00:21:48,833
Whenever you tell one of
your little ghost stories

517
00:21:48,916 --> 00:21:50,083
you attract low
level spirits,

518
00:21:50,166 --> 00:21:51,833
and they attract
stronger spirits...

519
00:21:51,916 --> 00:21:53,666
and then we're
in big trouble.

520
00:21:53,750 --> 00:21:55,708
So, when you entertain
yourselves with these stories

521
00:21:55,791 --> 00:21:57,041
you're putting me at risk.

522
00:21:57,125 --> 00:21:58,291
Oh No.

